description: This is the home in Katy—truly one-of-a-kind. An elegant, light-filled single-story residence on a cul-de-sac, directly on the lake, complete with a sparkling pool in an exclusive gated community. Enjoy superior lake views from nearly every room. The flexible floor plan is remarkable, offering up to three studies, or the option of two studies plus an exercise room, or even a study with a tranquil gazing room—plus an additional bonus space. Outdoor living is just as impressive, with a covered patio by the pool overlooking the lake and fountain. The multi-level backyard features a paver walkway leading to a cozy seating area by the water. And the views? They’re nothing short of breathtaking. Truly, these are AMAZING VIEWS.
